{
  "texts": [
    "The participants are in the South Asian Region (Bangladesh, India), the Scandinavian Region (Finland, Norway), and USA.",
    "There were no specific reasons for choosing participants from these regions; instead, they were random.",
    "This section outlines the thematic analysis of the interview data.",
    "We also aligned these themes and subthemes with the study's research questions.",
    "The primary themes are (i) user requirements, (ii) explanation format, and (iii) impact of explainable recommendation."
  ]
}